00:02:20,300 --> 00:02:22,200
to the right with a large velocity,

60
00:02:22,200 --> 00:02:25,300
large means comparable to the speed of light,

61
00:02:25,300 --> 00:02:28,440
or some fraction of the speed of light,

62
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:32,160
then because of the Doppler effect,

63
