Yes,

75
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:02,040
this is true.

76
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:04,420
That is really the way it works.

77
00:03:05,760 --> 00:03:09,020
We are moving through the microwave background,

78
00:03:09,020 --> 00:03:10,160
our planet,

79
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:15,800
