But it has got to do

93
00:03:37,830 --> 00:03:39,660
with known motions of the Earth.

94
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:43,660
And so the answer is yes,

95
00:03:43,660 --> 00:03:45,280
there is such a Doppler effect,

96
00:03:45,440 --> 00:03:45,820
and yes,

97
00:03:45,820 --> 00:03:49,200
there is a preferred frame of reference.

98
